    "description": "<br><br>这个序章提供了“The Last Farmer”完整旅程的有限预览。踏入被遗忘的德克萨斯的阳光炙烤的广袤土地，体验坚韧和复兴的滋味。体验冒险的片段，不要忘记将完整游戏添加到愿望单，以获取完整体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119650/extras/7faba46677529bd22fd1d12ed96ccb4e.poster.avif?t=1728472341\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119650/extras/7faba46677529bd22fd1d12ed96ccb4e.webm?t=1728472341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119650/extras/7faba46677529bd22fd1d12ed96ccb4e.mp4?t=1728472341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>沉浸在严酷而美丽的沙漠农业世界中。学习收集露水，种植耐旱作物，并在充满挑战的景观中照料牲畜。资源管理至关重要，每一滴水和每一个决定都可能意味着生存或死亡的区别。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119650/extras/52330b0489c39dc8f4c5828b1785b5fe.poster.avif?t=1728472341\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119650/extras/52330b0489c39dc8f4c5828b1785b5fe.webm?t=1728472341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119650/extras/52330b0489c39dc8f4c5828b1785b5fe.mp4?t=1728472341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>用收集的材料从头开始建造你的家园，建造避难所、水系统和防御工事。面对无情的自然元素、掠夺的威胁和不断逼近的脱水危险。适应动态天气系统，从残酷的风暴到炙热的高温，每一种天气都会影响你的农业策略。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119650/extras/eb15f60af668adf64432aebca6297f5b.poster.avif?t=1728472341\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119650/extras/eb15f60af668adf64432aebca6297f5b.webm?t=1728472341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119650/extras/eb15f60af668adf64432aebca6297f5b.mp4?t=1728472341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>与稀少但至关重要的幸存者社区互动，交换货物、知识和故事。你的每一个行动都在塑造土地的复兴，通过沉浸式的第一人称游戏体验，让你感受到每一颗种子的种植和每一个决定的影响。<br><br>“The Last Farmer: Prologue”不仅仅是一款生存游戏；它是一段恢复的旅程，你的农场在荒凉中成为希望的象征。在这个有限版本中开始你的冒险，为完整游戏做好准备，在那里，沙漠的严酷将考验你的耐力，而你的农场的成功将播下新的开始的种子。<br><br>现在就投入这段旅程，成为土地的最后希望。将“The Last Farmer”添加到愿望单，以获得在被遗忘的德克萨斯沙漠中完整的生存、坚韧和复兴体验。",
